description.en: Full laundry renovation in Camberwell with floor-to-ceiling subway tiles, waterproofed flooring with anti-slip finish, custom splashback behind the trough, and seamless caulking around cabinetry and benchtops.
description.zh: Camberwell洗衣房全面翻新，通顶地铁砖铺贴、防水防滑地面、水槽后定制挡水板，以及橱柜和台面周边无缝密封处理。
